{"tid":1709484,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國政府 : 反對所有香港暴力.  請「中共」遵守《中英聯合聲明》","createTime":"2019-11-12T01:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T06:58:58.000Z","uid":134071,"like":197,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae9d7554ca50ee86d2cecb180008b673d2cd4f1","tid":1709484,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:46:42.000Z","msg":"聲明好過英國政府果篇多多聲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/statedeptspox/status/1194056791090507776\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstatedeptspox%2Fstatus%2F1194056791090507776&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYtHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=a8652b0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstatedeptspox%2Fstatus%2F1194056791090507776&h=5304e971\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/statedeptspox/status/1194056791090507776</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/f2mUBbu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff2mUBbu.jpg&h=7bc2e1ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"205391790586afc524919ce2eff00454898c3694","tid":1709484,"uid":134071,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:47:27.000Z","msg":"文字版<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.state.gov/situation-in-hong-kong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fsituation-in-hong-kong%2F&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYtHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=110ba110\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.state.gov/situation-in-hong-kong/</a><br />\n<br />\nSituation in Hong Kong<br />\nNovember 11, 2019<br />\n<br />\nThe United States is watching the situation in Hong Kong with grave concern.  &lrm;We condemn violence on all sides, extend our sympathies to victims of violence regardless of their political inclinations, and call for all parties&mdash; police and protestors&mdash; to exercise restraint.&lrm;  We repeat President Trump&rsquo;s call for a humane resolution to the protests.<br />\n<br />\nThe increased polarization within Hong Kong society underscores the need for a broad-based and sincere dialogue between the government, protestors, and citizenry writ large.  The United States urges the Hong Kong government to build on its dialogue with the Hong Kong public and begin efforts to address the underlying concerns driving the protests.  We also urge the protestors to respond to efforts at dialogue.<br />\n<br />\nThe United States believes that Hong Kong&rsquo;s autonomy, its adherence to the rule of law, and its commitment to protecting civil liberties are key to preserving its special status under U.S. law, as well as to the success of &ldquo;One Country, Two Systems&rdquo; and Hong Kong&rsquo;s future stability and prosperity.  We urge Beijing to honor the commitments it made in the Sino-British Joint Declaration, including commitments that Hong Kong will &ldquo;enjoy a high degree of autonomy&rdquo; and that the people of Hong Kong will enjoy human rights the freedoms of expression and peaceful assembly&mdash; core values that we share with Hong Kong."},{"pid":"b7d4a586826fb937b6ffca05718965ad4bc73fe2","tid":1709484,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae106f787828e0e50e8e9037f137f94b3e0f27b6","tid":1709484,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:49:11.000Z","msg":"英國政府: 關注香港示威者與警方暴力升級 , 令人深感不安 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1708933/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1708933/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"988a7a679b5e3065e0b18438106fb111baa61c80","tid":1709484,"uid":155095,"like":24,"disli